properties.description: Four wheel drive due to deep sand, deep gravel, and large boulders.  Great for hiking.

properties.description: Four wheel drive due to large boulders and deep gravel.  Great for hiking.

properties.name: Cottonwood/Marble Canyon Loop
properties.description: Cross country backpacking loop.  Route finding required.  No open fires.  Camp at least 100 yards away from water sources.
